33 INJURY OR DEATH.".
34 (b) A retail dealer who knowingly or intentionally violates
35 subsection (a) commits a Class C infraction. However, the violation
36 is a Class A infraction if the retail dealer has a prior unrelated
37 adjudication for the violation.
